

These two have never acted like this before, but it was probably because of their seething anger. Nevertheless, Oliver wanted to try speaking to them...but before he could even do so, he was suddenly lifted up, held back by Lutz, causing him to be immobilised. When he turned to Kuro...he saw him drawing his sword.


Oliver's eyes widened upon seeing this. He spoke in a weak voice, "Wh-What are you going to do.....?"


"We're going to kill you, of course."